data.description: This open concept home features a large great room which flows seamlessly into the kitchen. Kitchen has ample cabinets for storage. Kitchen appliances convey with sale. Primary bedroom is downstairs with a spacious walk-in closet. Laundry room &  bath downstairs. There are 3 guest bedrooms, a guest bath, plus a bonus room upstairs. Luxury vinyl flooring throughout the home. The back yard is a nice size with a new fence & pergola. Corner lot. Located in a desirable subdivision near parks, shopping centers and restaurants. Full remodel throughout home. Improvements includes Roof, AC Unit, Water Heater, Water Softener, Reverse Osmosis to name a few. Please note: Can't show on Mondays or Wednesday 12pm-4pm
